<p class="lead">The panel grid pattern arranges panel items in a column grid.</p>

<h2>Rules for the panel grid</h2>
<ul>
	<li>Panels must be arranged equally into two or three columns.</li>
	<li>Panel elements must never appear outside of a grid.</li>
	<li>There is no limitation on combination of colours used for panel headings.</li>
	<li>Panel headings must link to other webpages.</li>
	<li>Links must be used in an unordered list with no more than six links per panel.</li>
</ul>

